				<p class="nyt-article-byline">By MICHAEL J. DE LA MERCED</p>
				<p class="nyt-article-summary">Thanks to $500 million in investments in Alibaba made in 2011 and 2012, Silver Lake now sits on a stake worth more than $5.1 billion.</p>
			</div>
			<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">
			<div class="nyt-article-promo">
